        <mxCell id="-CxPptguk03cCc-DeKz5-1" parent="1" style="text;strokeColor=none;align=center;fillColor=none;html=1;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;movable=0;resizable=0;rotatable=0;deletable=0;editable=0;locked=1;connectable=0;fontSize=15;labelBackgroundColor=none;" value="$$ z = \frac{1}{3 - j \space 2} = \frac{1}{3 - j \space 2} \cdot \frac{3 + j \space 2}{3 + j \space 2} = \frac{3 + j \space 2}{3^2 + j \space 6&amp;nbsp; - j \space 6 - 2 \space j^2} = \frac{3 + j \space 2}{3^2 - 2 \space (-1)} = \frac{3 + j \space 2}{9 + 4} = \frac{3}{13} + j \space \frac{2}{13}$$" vertex="1">
